        "Title": "DuckTales (Woo-oo!)",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COLOMBIA",
        "PublicId": "112238621890",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/colombia/scene_hippo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5562b1ba-d12e-428d-886e-bc9f2c80c2f2).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning. I&apos;m Duck McMoney and I have a job for you... \r\rDeep in the Colombian jungle, there is a town known as Santa Fortuna, built on the remains of an Olmec temple. \r\rThere is a sacrificial knife in the nearby unexplored tunnel. I want it along with the shaman&apos;s blood on it. \r\rI also want you to get rid of my lavish nephews. They&apos;ve been pissing me off for too many years. \r\rRemember, \rMy friend, Gyro, will he waiting for you in the helicopter at the nearby helipad",
        "GameVersion": "8.7.0.0",
        "IsPublished": true,
